<div class='col-md-6'>
  <div class='well'>
    <h4><b><i>Invite players to play a Match!</i></b></h4>
 List of invitations for playing a match. Before sending an invitation to a group of players you choose the selection criteria (open or social, category, level, type of match,...).
 <br/>Remember! your email message will be sent initially to the first 25 players of your selected target group. This number will increase with your number of your played matches.
 <br/>You will receive From players, contacted via email or through here, answers and proposals for arranging easily and quickly the match. If you know some details (days, hours, court,...) you can publish them for facilitating other players to contact you and progress quickly to the match organisation. When the match has four players, you have to close the match invitation.
 </p>
 </div><!-- well -->
</div><!-- md-6 -->  
